basic.Peptide Name: Fa-AMP2 (Fagopyrum antimicrobial peptide 2; hevein-type; Plant defensin)
basic.Target Organism: Gram-positive bacteria:Clavibacter michiganensis (IC50=17 µg/ml), Curtobacterium accumfaciens (IC50=15 µg/ml);Gram-negative bacteria:Erwinia carotovora (IC50=15 µg/ml), Agrobacterium radiobacter (IC50=17 µg/ml), Agrobacterium rhizogenes (IC50=24 µg/ml).Fungi:Fusarium oxysporum (IC50=29 µg/ml), Geotrichum candidum (IC50=25 µg/ml).
